Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:15.07,Sora Eng Titles 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,268.75)}Telephone - Emergency Announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.07,0:24:11.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time :
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:12.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Telephone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:14.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared, my people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:40.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to move forward! Move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are our comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Left 40 degrees! Prepare to fire from the main artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:57.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance 400! Gun loader, Load HEAT round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Olga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:03.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been confined to this tank for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die before I get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, inform the reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:22.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We destroyed one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:26.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia, please screen Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's flashing out there, but it's not lightning, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On our t-three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:45.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs39.999998}TL Note: Hawkers in Japan usually have their own unique song that attracts people to buy their goods. Here, the song is in pieces so it's hard to translate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:38.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:45.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bamboo strip...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:24.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël! You have to press harder to get it washed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:54.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's cold in this building during winter, it's so nice to have a cool summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:58.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I thought it was Rio-senpai's turn to do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that she's pretty busy, so we took her turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:08.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she had no appetite and we should eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:17.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Dinner preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And... What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you play with food, you'll get stung by a bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am not playing with it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:29.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs39.999998}Obon is a traditional Oriental festival. The gate between Earth and the afterlife opens on the 15th day of the 7th month of the lunar calendar allowing ghosts come to Earth. People worship the ghosts to prevent them from harming people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the Obon Festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? What is Obon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta de Lumière.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:37.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta de Lumière is a local festival in southern Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:44.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is based on a folk belief, which says that the souls of the dead return to the real world during a certain period of time in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:48.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a sign of sending these souls back, people let lanterns float in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In different areas, the same festival is also sometimes called Obon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then it's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The souls will return...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean that ghosts will come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it must be so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we do have some kinds of fire lighting back in my hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:21.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who passed away will go to heaven, and will always be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who wander the earth must be the bad ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:28.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, lend us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:36.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, when did you go out to do shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked delicious, so I bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong, priest-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy and mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:11.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? So it's even approved by the church? That fi...whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:15.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If this was the central diocese, it would be largely disputed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sloppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:27.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my hometown, we make horses and cows out of cucumbers and eggplants for our ancestors to ride on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:34.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in order to comfort the returning ancestors, people will dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you also make those things, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm. We only watched them last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:58.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,‏It is also a part of our job to maintain good relations with the local people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:03.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you forget about the stranger parts of it, then it's nothing but a beautiful festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Felicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:20.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just screwed up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:38.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty rare for the platoon leader to make such a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As she's not Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:45.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? We've had several pretty hot days recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rest a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:02.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The platoon leader seems weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:07.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just leaving her meal, but also buying watermelons without thinking about our food budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:10.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be going through something. Even if it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that I should have... Let me go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that she doesn't want anybody to even touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I read her record.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about it firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that position. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:12.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the monster which looks like the platoon leader came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:24.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that once upon a time, there used to be a lot of creatures living in the sea here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is marching toward its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We, humanity, will end up being totally destroyed one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... only a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:45.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's true, then what are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I... am still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if I could read your last words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... from the old time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:18.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Olga, Maslina, Anna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:29.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:37.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? I didn't know there were still people living in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... do you apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... {\alpha&HFF&}we lost... to those damn things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:56.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... we lost... {\alpha&HFF&}to those damn things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... we lost... to those damn things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't protect you from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are what remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the last bubble of hope for saving the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:42.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for humanity to return the world to its former prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just come to whatever conclusion you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world full of all the dregs left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:59.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Living sadly in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be too lonely for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:03.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any meaning in living in a world like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive! Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:22.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my troop could have arrived half a day earlier, it wouldn't have turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your majesty, Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a little bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:40.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you ignored Fiesta de Lumière last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's changed in your heart this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice color!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just bought it from the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, beautiful, beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:07.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt, that person used to be my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:13.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about protecting the people in the country, just like that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sometimes think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:29.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if she's really coming back, I want to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:35.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of talking about this, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I am worrying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good for a platoon leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even me... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't bear that burden alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I can be a good listener!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me be spoiled by your words and tell you all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:09.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worrying about getting "summer fat".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things continue like this, I won't be able to wear my winter clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:19.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that if you only eat watermelons, you will get thinner, so I gave it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, what's wrong with you, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still being absent-minded!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one at the Vingt Battle Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I was reliving that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guessed wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan also made one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really believe in souls at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a mission. Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san, who are you sending back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:21.17,Omiguchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,235)}Yukika Miyaaka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:21.17,Omiguchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,287)}Maslina Sysony
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:21.17,Omiguchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,348)}Olga Tolstaya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:21.17,Omiguchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,399)}Anna Blume
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:21.17,Omiguchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(682,453)}Something like Dupont
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:21.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues from the past, and a soldier whose name I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:25.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These people helped me learn what's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean, that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are worrying about anything, I... {\alpha&HFF&}\Nknow I might not be able to help at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are worrying about anything, I... \Nknow I might not be able to help at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you are worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san's always been worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I made you worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I love Felicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:24.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are never afraid to say what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:40.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia... me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:49.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How adorable... you all are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back again next year, ancestor-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:37.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rio, you just asked if there's any meaning in this world, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:43.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one that survived. I've been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:47.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one who survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that there can't be any meaning in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't that beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:08.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, if there isn't any, I can search for it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:17.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the reason why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... and then at that time the bishop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:22.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then? Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:25.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shitty Yumina-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:33.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let those kids have the same thoughts that I had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:35.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
